&quot;Well, my plan was to sneak up on them and scare the hell out of Whizbang. They were all together, they ran off pretty much in a straight line. I am just about to break my invisibility spell and give the old man a heart attack when they are suddenly surrounded by about 10 of those giants.&quot;<br>
